<h1 class="content-header">Trade gold, coins and jewelry with ease.</h1>
        <div class="pad-box pure-g">
            <div class="pad-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">

                <h3>
                    Specialized marketplace
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Search Global. Shop Local. Browse online inventories of established gold sellers. Buyers can find exactly what they want, for the price they want, before arriving in store.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pad-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3>
                    Sell with confidence
